        <title>Bastion</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/images/bastion/infocard.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&quot;initial-scan&quot;&gt;Initial Scan&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-plaintext&quot; data-lang=&quot;plaintext&quot;&gt;root@kali:~/HTB/Bastion# nmap -sV -sC 10.10.10.134 -oA bastion.nmap                                                                 
